{{Otheruses|Lok}}
'''Lok Pirate's Cant''' was an artificial language developed by [[Pirate/Legends|pirates]] and [[Mercenary/Legends|mercenaries]] living on [[Planet/Legends|planet]] [[Lok/Legends|Lok]] during the [[Galactic Republic/Legends|Old Republic]].

It was a specialized language, so it could not be used in all the situations or to convey all kinds of information.

